{"lemma":"جَمِيلُو","slug":"جَمِيلُو","root":"ج.م.ل","root_slug":"ج-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَمِيل","root":"جمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","name","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6354"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"beautiful","examples":[{"text":"زَرْتُ مَكَانًا جَمِيلًا وَمُثِيرًا لِلْإِعْجَابِ فِي رِحْلَتِي.","english":"I visited a beautiful and stunning place on my trip"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"pretty"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"handsome, fair, elegant"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"well-bred, of good manners","examples":[{"text":"أَيُّهَٰذَا الشَّاكِي وَمَا بِكَ دَاءٌ\nكُنْ جَمِيلًا تَرَ الْوُجُودَ جَمِيلًا\nʔayyuhāḏā š-šākī wamā bika dāʔun","english":"O! who be this complainant, and what is thine ailment?\nBe courteous [thyself! and] thou shall see a beautiful existence."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"good, excellent"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Jamil or Jameel, feminine equivalent جَمِيلَة (jamīla)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"good deed, favor, benefit","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"good quality","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"melted fat","tags":["uncountable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.miːl/","/ɡa.miːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6354","headword_ar":"جَمِيلٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Melted fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melting fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat that is melted and collected:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat that is melted, and, whenever it drips, made to drip upon bread, and then replaced over the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that it may drip again:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamala","text_ar":"جَمَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAlapN","text_ar":"جُمَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies [the same; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melted grease."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, * TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamuwlN","text_ar":"جَمُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Hence, accord. to Abu-l-'Alà, because, when a man becomes fat and in good condition, his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAl","text_ar":"جَمَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"becomes apparent, (Ham p. 155,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAlN","text_ar":"جُمَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAlN","text_ar":"جُمَّالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or this last denotes a higher degree of beauty than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Sgh,) and has no broken pl., (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajomalu","text_ar":"اَجْمَلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beautiful, goodly, comely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good in action,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) or also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in moral character:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [like the Greek"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"καλὸς","text_ar":"καλὸς","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":", the Latin"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulcher,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the French"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beau,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasanN","text_ar":"حَسَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pretty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"minutely, beautiful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"characterized by much goodness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comeliness, in his mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"characterized by much goodness communicated from him to others:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylapN","text_ar":"جَمِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) applied to a woman; (S, Mgh, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamolaA='u","text_ar":"جَمْلَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, K,) [said to be] an instance of [the measure]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaA='u","text_ar":"فَعْلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"having no [masc. of the measure]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoEalu","text_ar":"اَفْعَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [but see above;] or this is applied to any female as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complete, in body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A@ll~`ha","text_ar":"اـِنَّ ا@للّٰهَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN yuHib~u AljimaAla","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ يُحِبُّ الجِمَالَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily God is comely in deeds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an Abundant Bestower of good things: He loveth those who are of the like character."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmalahu","text_ar":"عَامَلَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAljamiyli","text_ar":"بَالجَمِيلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He treated him with comely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing, behaviour"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAsaHahu biAljamiyl","text_ar":"مَاسَحَهُ بِالجَمِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He coaxed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wheedled him, with comely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing, behaviour"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISd, K. [See 3.]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw jamiylK","text_ar":"اَبُو جَمِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The kind of plants called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albaqol","text_ar":"البَقْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because they embellish by their presence, and render good, the seasoning of food; or because they take away the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyl","text_ar":"جَمِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., the grease of the flesh-meat, and dry up the food. (Har p. 227.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","TA","Sgh","M","Msb","Ks"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}